These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: colombian, indian, spanish, dutch, polish, chinese, mexican
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: skateboarding, ice-hockey, tennis, swimming, lacrosse, cricket, golf
 1. the colombian is between the dutch and the mexican##2
 2. the indian is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the polish is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the dutch##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is tennis##2
 8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the mexican##1
 9. the polish is on the left of the chinese##1
10. the polish is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
11. the chinese is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | dutch | colombian | mexican | indian    | spanish | polish   | chinese    |
| Sport         | cricket  | ice-hockey   | swimming | skateboarding | tennis   | golf | lacrosse |

