.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, kale, pineapple, peas, raspberry, papaya, tomato
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, egyptian, thai, french, american, brazilian, indian
1. the brazilian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating papaya and the brazilian##2
3. the egyptian is on the right of the nigerian##1
4. the person eating tomato is on the right of the thai##1
5. the person eating kale is in the middle##1
6. the american is on the left of the nigerian##1
7. the indian is on the left of the person eating kale##1
8. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the french##1
9. the person eating peas is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | raspberry | pineapple | papaya | kale | tomato | broccoli      | peas  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | french  | indian     | thai     | american  | nigerian | egyptian |

