.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: british, thai, egyptian, italian, brazilian, french, turkish
7 different pets are kept: bird, cat, frog, horse, snake, goldfish, chinchilla
 1. the brazilian is on the left of the british##1
 2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the owner of the snake is the turkish##1
 4. the egyptian is on the left of the french##1
 5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 6. the italian is the owner of the horse##1
 7. the british is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the chinchilla and the italian##2
 9. the british is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
10. the thai is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | turkish | brazilian | british | thai   | italian | egyptian | french |
| Pet           | snake | goldfish     | cat     | frog | horse   | bird   | chinchilla    |

