.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, soy-milk, milk, cola, mirinda, 7up
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, spanish, turkish, argentine, thai, canadian, dutch
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the turkish##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the thai##1
 3. the canadian is on the right of the argentine##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the thai##1
 5. the indian is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the argentine is between the person drinking soy-milk and the canadian##2
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle##1
 8. the argentine is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is the spanish##1
10. the indian is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | cola  | milk  | almond-milk  | 7up      | mirinda       | coffee |
| Nationality   | thai | argentine | canadian | dutch | indian | turkish | spanish  |

