.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, country, techno, funk, d&b, trance, dubstep
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, quad-bike, tram, snowmobile, roller, trike
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of country##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the fan of dubstep and the fan of reggae##2
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
8. the person driving the subway is the fan of funk##1
9. the fan of d&b is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | d&b | reggae | techno | dubstep      | country      | trance |
| Transport     | subway | roller | trike       | jet-ski | quad-bike | snowmobile | tram |

