.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dressmaker, designer, fisherman, electrician, librarian, doctor, social-worker
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming, weightlifting, rugby, baseball, golf, skateboarding
1. the fisherman is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the librarian##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the designer is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the doctor is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is baseball and the dressmaker##2
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
8. the doctor is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | librarian | dressmaker | electrician | doctor | designer | fisherman     | social-worker |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | rugby    | skateboarding    | baseball      | swimming  | biathlon | golf |

