.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite, juice, water
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, badminton, soccer, skateboarding, biathlon, snowboarding, climbing
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking sprite##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is climbing##2
 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person drinking sprite##2
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | 7up | tea    | soy-milk | mirinda   | juice | water    | sprite |
| Sport      | skateboarding | golf | climbing    | badminton | biathlon    | soccer | snowboarding  |

