The people have 7 different jobs:  manager, designer, musician, project-manager, freelancer, social-worker, firefighter
 1. the freelancer is on the left of the project-manager##1
 2. the manager is on the left of the musician##1
 3. the social-worker is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 5. the freelancer is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 7. the designer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 8. the manager is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking 7up##2
11. the freelancer is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | sprite  | soy-milk   | 7up         | coffee     | almond-milk              | milk    | tea     |
| Job        | social-worker | designer | freelancer | project-manager | firefighter | manager | musician |

