.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: spy, musical, zombie, martial-arts, crime, mystery, comedy
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, airplane, van, ship, bike, subway, snowmobile
1. the person watching spy movies is the person driving the subway##1
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is between the person driving the snowmobile and the person driving the bike##2
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is in the middle##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
8. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
