.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, sprite, iced-tea, soy-milk, juice
The people have 7 different hobbies: collecting, dancing, chess, camping, sudoku, card-games, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
8. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | lemonade       | juice         | iced-tea         | sprite   | almond-milk        | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | fishing | chess | collecting | sudoku | dancing | card-games | camping  |

