 4. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching action movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 5. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 7. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is the fan of country##1
 9. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
10. the fan of r&b is the person watching time-travel movies##1

