 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 6. the person eating lime is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person drinking potatoade is the person eating mango##1
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking 7up and the person eating lime##2
