 7. the person eating pepper is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person eating banana is the person eating banana##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating apple##1
10. the person eating banana is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
